author: Peter Marsh
title: Live: Human trials of COVID-19 vaccine begin in UK, National Cabinet slated to meet
description: The first of 500 volunteers receive injections of a potential coronavirus vaccine in the UK, while a debrief on the infection rate in Australia is expected later today. Follow live.
content:
Posted

The first of 500 volunteers have received injections of a potential coronavirus vaccine in the UK, but participants won't be deliberately exposed to the virus.
